column16: Jason Bay out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Adam Jones.   Kendrys Morales scores.
Michael Morse flies out to right fielder Nick Markakis.   Kendrys Morales to 3rd.
Kendrys Morales doubles (6) on a line drive to center fielder Adam Jones.   Michael Saunders scores.    Kyle Seager scores.
Kyle Seager singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Adam Jones.   Michael Saunders to 2nd.
Michael Saunders singles on a ground ball to center fielder Adam Jones.
Robert Andino grounds out to first baseman Chris Davis.
Jesus Montero called out on strikes.
Justin Smoak grounds out, second baseman Ryan Flaherty to first baseman Chris Davis.
